lead_paragraph: A fluent unbroken third-wicket partnership of 114 between Jos Buttler and Eoin Morgan carried England to an emphatic eight-wicket victory over Sri Lanka in a one-off Twenty20 international on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Buttler, Morgan Lead England to Crushing T20 Win
